        "title": 		"Storing your passwords",
        "body": <<<"
			<p>There are multiple methods of storing your passwords. There are different benefits and drawbacks to using different methods, but all have been used safely over time. The safest method is the one that meets the security requirements for your organisation and are convenient for you - so you don’t undermine your own security with less safe shortcuts (like sticky notes or reusing passwords).</p>

			<p>Let’s look at some of the more popular and safer methods.</p>
