				"title": "Tips for using this password storage technique",
				"body": <<<"
					<p><strong>Buy a Ready-Made Password Journal:</strong> Purchase a dedicated password journal designed for security, which often includes features like tips for creating strong passwords and organised sections for different accounts.</p>

					<p><strong>Store in a Secure Yet Accessible Place:</strong> Keep the password book in a locked drawer at home. For added security, consider using a small personal safe.</p>
